---
title: Spiced Chicken, Chickpeas and Spinach with Fluffy Cilantro Rice and Yogurt Sauce
description: This supper is packed with chickpeas, chicken and Indian-style spices. Fluffy rice is the perfect base for this curry and cooling yogurt brings it all together!

